; Coverage test for amount.cc lines 1043-1055
; Exercise trailing period in amount parsing (hledger compatibility)
; A trailing decimal point with no following digits indicates zero decimal
; places, used by hledger to disambiguate decimal marks from digit group marks

commodity $1,000.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food            $1,234.
    Assets:Cash

test bal
             $-1,234  Assets:Cash
              $1,234  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
